msgstr ""
"Nakonfigurujte **Employment Hero API** přechodem do "
":menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfigurace --> Nastavení`. Další pole se "
"zobrazí po kliknutí na :guilabel:`Povolit integraci Employment Hero`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:0
msgid ""
"Enabling Employment Hero Integration in Odoo Accounting displays new fields "
"in the\n"
"settings"
msgstr ""
"Povolení integrace Employment Hero v Odoo Accounting zobrazí nová pole v "
"nastavení"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:28
