#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off.rst:485
msgid "Mandatory days"
msgstr "Obligatoriske dage"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off.rst:487
msgid ""
"Some companies have special days where specific departments, or the entire "
"staff, is required to be present, and time off is not allowed on those "
"specific days."
msgstr ""
"Nogle virksomheder har særlige dage, hvor specifikke afdelinger eller hele "
"personalet er forpligtet til at være til stede, og fri er ikke tilladt på "
"disse specifikke dage."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off.rst:490
msgid ""
"These types of days are called *mandatory days* in Odoo. These can be "
"configured to be company-wide, or department specific. When configured, "
"employees in the specified department or company are unable to submit time "
"off requests for these mandatory days."
msgstr ""
"Disse typer dage kaldes *obligatoriske dage* i Odoo. Disse kan konfigureres "
"til at være virksomhedsdækkende eller afdelingsspecifikke. Når de er "
"konfigureret, kan medarbejdere i den angivne afdeling eller virksomhed ikke "
"indsende anmodninger om fri på disse obligatoriske dage."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off.rst:495
msgid "Create mandatory days"
msgstr "Opret obligatoriske dage"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off.rst:497
msgid ""
"No mandatory days are configured in Odoo by default. To create a mandatory "
"day, navigate to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> Configuration --> "
"Mandatory Days`."
msgstr ""
"Žádné povinné dny nejsou v Odoo nastaveny standardně. Chcete-li vytvořit "
"povinný den, přejděte na :menuselection:`aplikace Fri --> Konfigurace --> "
"Povinné dny`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off.rst:500
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`New` button in the top-left corner, and a blank line "
"appears in the list."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na tlačítko :guilabel:`Nový` v levém horním rohu a v seznamu se "
"zobrazí prázdný řádek."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off.rst:504
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: Enter the name of the mandatory day."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Název`: Zadejte název povinného dne."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off.rst:505
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: If in a multi-company database, this field is visible, "
"and the current company populates this field, by default. Using the drop-"
"down menu, select the company the mandatory day is for."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Společnost`: V případě databáze s více společnostmi je toto pole "
